languages: Custom: separate multiple values with commas, e.g. `en-US,en,zh-CN,zh`. The first value is treated as the preferred language.
desc.canvas: Canvas fingerprinting detects device traits by analyzing subtle differences in how graphics are drawn.
desc.audio: Audio fingerprinting identifies your device through unique patterns in audio signal processing.
desc.webgl: WebGL fingerprinting captures device characteristics based on variations in 3D rendering behavior.
webrtc: Block websites from accessing your real IP address via WebRTC—especially useful when using a proxy. Helps prevent IP leaks.
Disabling this may cause certain websites to malfunction or behave unexpectedly.
desc.fonts: Font fingerprinting reveals device details by checking which fonts are supported and how they’re rendered.
desc.webgpu: WebGPU fingerprinting extracts device information by analyzing differences in GPU processing capabilities.
desc.domRect: DOMRect fingerprinting gathers device data by measuring variations in element positioning and dimensions.
desc.seed: Global Seed, Acts on **Random by Global Seed** Options
inject-mode: Enable for faster script injection (requires browser support); disable to use compatibility mode.
`chrome 138+` Enable the **Allow script injection** option on the extension details page

err.input-hostname: Please enter the correct domain name
err.input-port: Please enter the correct port number
err.ns-fast-inject: Failed to enable, please check the config documentation

if.remove-parent-domain: Whether to remove its parent domain
if.remove-child-domain: Whether to remove its child domain
if.config-import: Whether to overwrite the current config
if.clean-whitelist: Whether to clean the current whitelist

status.unknown: Not supported by current browser version

desc.userScripts: Allow the extension to use the **userScripts** permission to make the extension adaptable to more sites

subscribe: When the extension loads, it will fetch configuration from the subscription target. It will overwrite the original settings and merge the whitelist. The configuration must be in JSON format. Refer to README.md for more details.
record: Record the call of fingerprint api, some api are often used when rendering elements, so the number of records for some api will be very large
Record the source address and number of iframe loaded
